  20 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audacious-0.1.2.ebuild,
  audacious-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  XMMS skin symlinking creates broken symlinks if the source dir is empty.
  Stop doing it now that an audacious-themes package is available. Closes bug
  #123458 by Georgi Georgiev <chutz@gg3.net>.

  19 Feb 2006; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  audacious-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc64.

  19 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -files/0.1-aac-makefile.am,
  -audacious-0.1.ebuild, -audacious-0.1-r1.ebuild, -audacious-0.1.1.ebuild,
  -audacious-0.2.ebuild, audacious-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Remove stale ebuilds and patches. Add taglib dependency for musepack as
  suggested by frirajder@gmail.com, closes bug #123378.

  18 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +files/0.2-segfault.diff,
  +files/0.2-thumbnail.diff, audacious-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Two additional patches submitted, closes bugs #123312 & #123313. Thanks to
  Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> & Daniel Drake <dsd@gentoo.org>.

*audacious-0.2-r1 (18 Feb 2006)

  18 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  +files/0.2-no-sigabrt-on-null-path.diff, +audacious-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Do not abort when path == NULL, patch by Daniel Drake <dsd@gentoo.org>.
  Closes bug #123301.

  02 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> audacious-0.2.ebuild:
  Dependency update; GTK+ 2.6 is required by the 0.2 release.

